<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[الدَّجْدَجَة]</span> دَجْدَجَ الليلُ: أي أَظْلم.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">ودَجْدجْتُ بالدّجاجة:</span> إِذا صِحْت بها.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[خ]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[الدَّخْدَخَةُ]</span>،<span class="c5"> بالخاء معجمةً:</span> التَّذْليل.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">يقال:</span> دَخْدَخْنَا القومَ: أي ذللناهم.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وقال الشيباني:</span> الدَّخْدَخَة: الإِعياء.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[الدَّرْدَرَةُ]</span> دَرْدَرَ الصبيُّ البُسْرة: إِذا لاكَها.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
